<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>MindBloom — Longevity by Design. Energy by Nature.</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fraunces:ital,opsz,wght@0,9..144,300;0,9..144,400;0,9..144,500;0,9..144,600;1,9..144,400&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root{
    --green:#2d3a2c;
    --green-deep:#1d2620;
    --cream:#ede7da;
    --navy:#232c3a;
    --gold:#c7a04e;
    --gold-soft:#d9bd84;
    --ink:#15140f;
    --ink-soft:#211f17;
    --paper:#f6f2e8;
    --paper-dim:#e7e0d0;
    --line: rgba(199,160,78,0.28);
  }
  *{box-sizing:border-box; margin:0; padding:0;}
  html{scroll-behavior:smooth;}
  body{
    font-family:'Inter', sans-serif;
    background:var(--paper);
    color:var(--ink);
    -webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;
  }
  img{display:block; max-width:100%; height:auto;}
  a{color:inherit; text-decoration:none;}
  .eyebrow{
    font-family:'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size:0.72rem;
    letter-spacing:0.22em;
    text-transform:uppercase;
    font-weight:600;
    color:var(--gold);
  }
  h1,h2,h3{font-family:'Fraunces', serif; font-weight:500; line-height:1.1; letter-spacing:-0.01em;}
  .rule{width:48px; height:1px; background:var(--gold); margin:18px 0;}
  .btn{
    display:inline-block;
    padding:14px 30px;
    background:var(--gold);
    color:var(--ink);
    font-family:'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size:0.78rem;
    letter-spacing:0.12em;
    text-transform:uppercase;
    font-weight:600;
    border:1px solid var(--gold);
    border-radius:2px;
    cursor:pointer;
    transition:background 0.25s, color 0.25s;
  }
  .btn:hover{background:transparent; color:var(--gold);}
  .btn-outline{
    background:transparent;
    color:var(--paper);
    border:1px solid rgba(246,242,232,0.4);
  }
  .btn-outline:hover{background:rgba(246,242,232,0.08); color:var(--paper);}

  /* ---------- NAV ---------- */
  nav{
    position:fixed; top:0; left:0; right:0; z-index:100;
    display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between;
    padding:22px 48px;
    background:linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(21,20,15,0.55), transparent);
    transition:background 0.3s, padding 0.3s;
  }
  nav.scrolled{ background:var(--ink); padding:14px 48px; box-shadow:0 2px 18px rgba(0,0,0,0.2); }
  .nav-logo{ display:flex; align-items:center; gap:12px; }
  .nav-logo img{ width:34px; height:34px; border-radius:50%; object-fit:cover; }
  .nav-logo span{
    font-family:'Inter', sans-serif; font-weight:600; font-size:1rem;
    letter-spacing:0.18em; color:var(--paper);
  }
  .nav-links{ display:flex; align-items:center; gap:36px; }
  .nav-links a{
    font-size:0.78rem; letter-spacing:0.1em; text-transform:uppercase;
    color:var(--paper); opacity:0.85; font-weight:500;
  }
  .nav-links a:hover{opacity:1; color:var(--gold-soft);}
  .cart-icon{ width:18px; height:18px; }
  .nav-mobile-toggle{ display:none; color:var(--paper); font-size:1.4rem; cursor:pointer; }

  /* ---------- HERO ---------- */
  .hero{
    position:relative; height:92vh; min-height:620px;
    display:flex; align-items:flex-end;
    background:url('https://pub-cc523e0480124a5e8d50ce67108ed9e1.r2.dev/Hero-MB-1.jpg') center center/cover no-repeat;
  }
  .hero::after{
    content:''; position:absolute; inset:0;
    background:linear-gradient(to top, rgba(15,14,10,0.82) 0%, rgba(15,14,10,0.32) 50%, rgba(15,14,10,0.05) 78%);
  }
  .hero-inner{ position:relative; z-index:2; padding:0 48px 80px; max-width:720px; }
  .hero h1{ font-size:3.6rem; color:var(--paper); margin-top:14px; }
  .hero p{ font-size:1.05rem; line-height:1.7; color:var(--paper); opacity:0.82; max-width:480px; margin:22px 0 32px; }

  /* ---------- BRAND STORY ---------- */
  .story{ background:var(--green-deep); color:var(--paper); padding:48px; }
  .story-grid{
    max-width:1240px; margin:0 auto;
    display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 0.8fr; gap:80px; align-items:center;
  }
  .story h2{ font-size:2.2rem; color:var(--paper); margin:14px 0 24px; }
  .story p{ font-size:1.02rem; line-height:1.8; opacity:0.78; max-width:460px; }

  .benefit-row{
    max-width:1240px; margin:70px auto 0;
    display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);
    border-top:1px solid var(--line); padding-top:42px;
  }
  .benefit-item{ padding-right:24px; }
  .benefit-item svg{ width:26px; height:26px; stroke:var(--gold); margin-bottom:14px; }
  .benefit-item h4{
    font-family:'Inter', sans-serif; font-size:0.85rem; letter-spacing:0.08em;
    text-transform:uppercase; font-weight:600; margin-bottom:6px;
  }
  .benefit-item p{ font-size:0.85rem; opacity:0.6; line-height:1.5; max-width:none; }

  /* ---------- SHOP GRID ---------- */
  .shop{ padding:120px 48px; max-width:1280px; margin:0 auto; }
  .shop-head{ text-align:center; max-width:560px; margin:0 auto 64px; }
  .shop-head h2{ font-size:2.4rem; margin:14px 0 16px; }
  .shop-head p{ font-size:1rem; line-height:1.7; opacity:0.65; }
  .shop-grid{ display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr); gap:36px; }
  .product-card{
    background:var(--paper-dim); border-radius:3px; overflow:hidden;
    border:1px solid rgba(45,58,44,0.1);
    transition:transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
  }
  .product-card:hover{ transform:translateY(-6px); box-shadow:0 22px 40px rgba(21,20,15,0.14); }
  .product-card .pc-img{ height:380px; overflow:hidden; background:var(--ink); }
  .product-card .pc-img img{ width:100%; height:100%; object-fit:cover; }
  .pc-body{ padding:26px 24px 30px; }
  .pc-tag{ font-size:0.7rem; letter-spacing:0.14em; text-transform:uppercase; color:var(--green); font-weight:600; }
  .pc-body h3{ font-size:1.3rem; margin:8px 0 4px; }
  .pc-flavor{ font-size:0.82rem; opacity:0.55; margin-bottom:14px; }
  .pc-foot{ display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between; margin-top:18px; }
  .pc-price{ font-weight:600; font-size:0.95rem; }
  .pc-link{ font-size:0.74rem; letter-spacing:0.1em; text-transform:uppercase; font-weight:600; color:var(--green); border-bottom:1px solid var(--green); padding-bottom:2px; }

  /* ---------- PRODUCT DETAIL / GALLERY ---------- */
  .pdp{ background:var(--paper-dim); padding:110px 48px 130px; }
  .pdp-inner{ max-width:1280px; margin:0 auto; }
  .pdp-eyebrow{ text-align:left; margin-bottom:8px; }
  .pdp-grid{ display:grid; grid-template-columns:96px 1fr 0.78fr; gap:28px; margin-top:30px; align-items:start; }

  .thumb-rail{ display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:14px; }
  .thumb{
    width:96px; height:120px; border-radius:2px; overflow:hidden; cursor:pointer;
    border:2px solid transparent; opacity:0.6; transition:opacity 0.2s, border-color 0.2s;
    background:var(--ink); position:relative;
  }
  .thumb.active, .thumb:hover{ opacity:1; border-color:var(--gold); }
  .thumb img{ width:100%; height:100%; object-fit:cover; }
  .thumb-label{
    position:absolute; bottom:0; left:0; right:0; padding:5px 6px;
    background:rgba(21,20,15,0.7); color:var(--paper);
    font-size:0.56rem; letter-spacing:0.05em; text-transform:uppercase; text-align:center;
  }

  .viewer{
    position:relative; border-radius:3px; overflow:hidden;
    background:var(--ink); aspect-ratio:555/843; max-height:780px;
  }
  .viewer-pane{ position:absolute; inset:0; display:none; }
  .viewer-pane.active{ display:block; }
  .viewer-pane img{ width:100%; height:100%; object-fit:cover; }

  /* composited proof-content pane */
  .proof-pane{ position:relative; }
  .proof-pane img{ width:100%; height:100%; object-fit:cover; }
  .proof-overlay{
    position:absolute; top:0; right:0; bottom:0; width:58%;
    background:linear-gradient(to right, rgba(21,20,15,0) 0%, rgba(21,20,15,0.55) 18%, rgba(21,20,15,0.86) 42%, rgba(21,20,15,0.9) 100%);
    display:flex; flex-direction:column; justify-content:center;
    padding:8% 7% 8% 16%;
    color:var(--paper);
  }
  .proof-overlay .po-logo{ display:flex; align-items:center; gap:10px; margin-bottom:18px; }
  .proof-overlay .po-logo img{ width:32px; height:32px; border-radius:50%; }
  .proof-overlay .po-logo span{ font-size:0.78rem; letter-spacing:0.2em; font-weight:600; }
  .proof-overlay h3{ font-size:1.5rem; color:var(--paper); margin-bottom:10px; }
  .proof-overlay .po-sub{ font-size:0.92rem; opacity:0.8; padding-bottom:18px; margin-bottom:18px; border-bottom:1px solid rgba(199,160,78,0.3); }
  .po-row{ display:flex; gap:14px; padding:16px 0; border-bottom:1px solid rgba(199,160,78,0.18); }
  .po-row:last-child{ border-bottom:none; }
  .po-row svg{ width:26px; height:26px; stroke:var(--gold); flex-shrink:0; margin-top:2px; }
  .po-row strong{ display:block; font-size:0.8rem; letter-spacing:0.06em; text-transform:uppercase; margin-bottom:4px; }
  .po-row p{ font-size:0.85rem; opacity:0.75; line-height:1.5; }

  /* motion pending pane */
  .motion-pane{
    background:linear-gradient(135deg, var(--green-deep), var(--ink) 70%);
    color:var(--paper); text-align:center; padding:0 14%;
  }
  .viewer-pane.motion-pane.active{
    display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; flex-direction:column;
  }
  .motion-play{
    width:64px; height:64px; border-radius:50%; border:1.5px solid var(--gold);
    display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; margin-bottom:22px;
  }
  .motion-play svg{ width:20px; height:20px; fill:var(--gold); margin-left:3px; }
  .motion-pane h3{ color:var(--paper); font-size:1.3rem; margin-bottom:10px; }
  .motion-pane p{ font-size:0.85rem; opacity:0.6; line-height:1.6; }

  .pdp-info{ padding-top:6px; }
  .pdp-info .pc-tag{ margin-bottom:10px; display:block; }
  .pdp-info h1{ font-size:2.1rem; margin-bottom:6px; }
  .pdp-info .flavor{ font-size:0.95rem; opacity:0.55; margin-bottom:20px; }
  .pdp-info .price{ font-size:1.2rem; font-weight:600; margin-bottom:26px; }
  .pdp-info .desc{ font-size:0.95rem; line-height:1.75; opacity:0.78; margin-bottom:30px; }
  .tag-row{ display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:8px; margin-bottom:34px; }
  .ingredient-tag{
    font-size:0.7rem; letter-spacing:0.06em; text-transform:uppercase; font-weight:600;
    padding:7px 13px; border:1px solid rgba(45,58,44,0.25); border-radius:20px; color:var(--green);
  }
  .pdp-cta{ display:flex; gap:14px; }
  .pdp-cta .btn{ flex:1; text-align:center; }

  /* ---------- FOOTER ---------- */
  footer{ background:var(--ink); color:var(--paper); padding:70px 48px 36px; }
  .footer-inner{ max-width:1280px; margin:0 auto; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:flex-end; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:30px; }
  .footer-logo{ display:flex; align-items:center; gap:12px; }
  .footer-logo img{ width:30px; height:30px; border-radius:50%; }
  .footer-logo span{ font-weight:600; letter-spacing:0.18em; font-size:0.92rem; }
  .footer-tag{ font-size:0.78rem; opacity:0.45; letter-spacing:0.08em; margin-top:10px; }
  .footer-meta{ font-size:0.74rem; opacity:0.4; letter-spacing:0.05em; }

  /* ---------- RESPONSIVE ---------- */
  @media (max-width: 980px){

    .benefit-row{ grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr); row-gap:30px; }
    .shop-grid{ grid-template-columns:1fr; }
    .pdp-grid{ grid-template-columns:1fr; }
    .thumb-rail{ flex-direction:row; overflow-x:auto; }
    .thumb{ flex:0 0 80px; height:100px; }
    .viewer{ aspect-ratio:4/3; max-height:520px; }
    .proof-overlay{ width:100%; padding:8% 8%; background:linear-gradient(to top, rgba(21,20,15,0.95) 0%, rgba(21,20,15,0.55) 55%, rgba(21,20,15,0) 100%); justify-content:flex-end; }
    .nav-links{ display:none; }
    .nav-mobile-toggle{ display:block; }
    .hero h1{ font-size:2.4rem; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<nav id="nav">
  <div class="nav-logo">
    <img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="MindBloom">
    <span>MINDBLOOM</span>
  </div>
  <div class="nav-links">
    <a href="#shop">Shop</a>
    <a href="#story">Our Story</a>
    <a href="#focus-clarity">Ingredients</a>
    <a href="#"><svg class="cart-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M6 7h12l-1 13H7L6 7z"/><path d="M9 7a3 3 0 0 1 6 0"/></svg></a>
  </div>
  <div class="nav-mobile-toggle">☰</div>
</nav>

<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-inner">
    <div class="eyebrow">Longevity by Design · Energy by Nature</div>
    <h1>Play the long game.</h1>
    <p>MindBloom is built for those who choose progress over shortcuts, and invest in a better tomorrow. Functional beverages built on adaptogens, nootropics, and electrolytes, for people who care more about the long term than a quick fix.</p>
    <a href="#shop" class="btn">Shop the Line</a>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="story" id="story">
  <div class="story-grid">
    <div>
      <div class="eyebrow">Rooted in Nature</div>
      <h2>Built for life, not just the next hour.</h2>
      <p>We source premium natural ingredients to support energy, focus, resilience, and healthy aging, so you can thrive for decades to come. Not just more years. Better years.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="benefit-row">
    <div class="benefit-item">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke-width="1.4"><path d="M3 18l5-9 4 6 3-5 6 8H3z"/></svg>
      <h4>Sustained Energy</h4>
      <p>No crashes, no jitters.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="benefit-item">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke-width="1.4"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="5"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="1.4"/></svg>
      <h4>Focus &amp; Clarity</h4>
      <p>Sharp mind, steady flow.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="benefit-item">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke-width="1.4"><path d="M12 3l7 3.5v5c0 5-3 8.5-7 9.5-4-1-7-4.5-7-9.5v-5L12 3z"/></svg>
      <h4>Resilience &amp; Recovery</h4>
      <p>Bounce back stronger.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="benefit-item">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke-width="1.4"><path d="M6 3h12M6 21h12M7 3c0 6 5 6 5 9s-5 3-5 9M17 3c0 6-5 6-5 9s5 3 5 9"/></svg>
      <h4>Built for the Long Haul</h4>
      <p>Support for every stage.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="shop" id="shop">
  <div class="shop-head">
    <div class="eyebrow">Shop The Line</div>
    <h2>Three states. One philosophy.</h2>
    <p>Each can is built around a single state of mind, with real botanicals doing the work, never a proprietary blend hiding what's inside.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="shop-grid">
    <div class="product-card">
      <div class="pc-img"><img src="https://pub-cc523e0480124a5e8d50ce67108ed9e1.r2.dev/MB-Green2.jpg" alt="MindBloom Focus + Clarity"></div>
      <div class="pc-body">
        <span class="pc-tag">Focus + Clarity</span>
        <h3>Citrus Basil</h3>
        <div class="pc-flavor">Sharp mind, steady flow.</div>
        <div class="pc-foot">
          <span class="pc-price">$6.99</span>
          <a href="#focus-clarity" class="pc-link">View Product</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="product-card">
      <div class="pc-img"><img src="https://pub-cc523e0480124a5e8d50ce67108ed9e1.r2.dev/MB-White2.jpg" alt="MindBloom Balance + Recovery"></div>
      <div class="pc-body">
        <span class="pc-tag">Balance + Recovery</span>
        <h3>Elderflower Ginger</h3>
        <div class="pc-flavor">Bounce back stronger.</div>
        <div class="pc-foot">
          <span class="pc-price">$6.99</span>
          <a href="#" class="pc-link">View Product</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="product-card">
      <div class="pc-img"><img src="https://pub-cc523e0480124a5e8d50ce67108ed9e1.r2.dev/MB-Blue2.jpg" alt="MindBloom Sustain + Energy"></div>
      <div class="pc-body">
        <span class="pc-tag">Sustain + Energy</span>
        <h3>Blackberry Rosemary</h3>
        <div class="pc-flavor">No crashes, no jitters.</div>
        <div class="pc-foot">
          <span class="pc-price">$6.99</span>
          <a href="#" class="pc-link">View Product</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="pdp" id="focus-clarity">
  <div class="pdp-inner">
    <div class="eyebrow pdp-eyebrow">Focus + Clarity · Citrus Basil</div>
    <h2 style="font-size:2rem;">A closer look at the world.</h2>

    <div class="pdp-grid">
      <div class="thumb-rail">
        <div class="thumb active" data-pane="p1"><img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="Product"><span class="thumb-label">Product</span></div>
        <div class="thumb" data-pane="p2"><img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="Proof content" style="object-position:left;"><span class="thumb-label">What's Inside</span></div>
        <div class="thumb" data-pane="p3"><img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="World still"><span class="thumb-label">The World</span></div>
        <div class="thumb" data-pane="p4"><img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="World still"><span class="thumb-label">In Motion</span></div>
      </div>

      <div class="viewer">
        <div class="viewer-pane active" id="p1"><img src="https://pub-cc523e0480124a5e8d50ce67108ed9e1.r2.dev/MB-Green2.jpg" alt="MindBloom Focus + Clarity"></div>

        <div class="viewer-pane proof-pane" id="p2">
          <img src="https://pub-cc523e0480124a5e8d50ce67108ed9e1.r2.dev/MB-Green2.jpg" alt="MindBloom Focus + Clarity ingredients">
          <div class="proof-overlay">
            <div class="po-logo"><img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt=""><span>MINDBLOOM</span></div>
            <h3>Focus &amp; Clarity</h3>
            <div class="po-sub">Sharp mind, steady flow.</div>
            <div class="po-row">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke-width="1.4"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="5"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="1.4"/></svg>
              <div><strong>Nootropics</strong><p>Support cognitive function, focus, and memory.</p></div>
            </div>
            <div class="po-row">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke-width="1.4"><path d="M3 18l5-9 4 6 3-5 6 8H3z"/></svg>
              <div><strong>Sustained Energy</strong><p>No crashes, no jitters.</p></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="viewer-pane" id="p3"><img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="The MindBloom world" style="object-fit:cover;"></div>

        <div class="viewer-pane motion-pane" id="p4">
          <div class="motion-play"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polygon points="6,4 20,12 6,20"/></svg></div>
          <h3>Motion loop in production</h3>
          <p>This is where the can-to-clarity loop lives once final motion is rendered. Reserved here to show the full array of what a build includes.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="pdp-info">
        <span class="pc-tag">Functional Beverage · 12 fl oz</span>
        <h1>Focus + Clarity</h1>
        <div class="flavor">Citrus Basil</div>
        <div class="price">$6.99</div>
        <p class="desc">Energy without anxiety. Focus without force. Built on L-theanine, paraxanthine, and lion's mane, dosed for clean clarity that lasts through the afternoon fog, not just past it.</p>
        <div class="tag-row">
          <span class="ingredient-tag">Nootropics</span>
          <span class="ingredient-tag">Adaptogens</span>
          <span class="ingredient-tag">Zero Sugar</span>
          <span class="ingredient-tag">Natural Ingredients</span>
        </div>
        <div class="pdp-cta">
          <button class="btn" style="flex:2;">Add to Cart</button>
          <button class="btn btn-outline" style="flex:1; color:var(--ink); border-color:rgba(45,58,44,0.3);">Subscribe</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<footer>
  <div class="footer-inner">
    <div>
      <div class="footer-logo"><img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="MindBloom"><span>MINDBLOOM</span></div>
      <div class="footer-tag">Longevity by design. Energy by nature.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="footer-meta">EST. 2024 — MindBloom</div>
  </div>
</footer>

<script>
  window.addEventListener('scroll', () => {
    document.getElementById('nav').classList.toggle('scrolled', window.scrollY > 60);
  });
  document.querySelectorAll('.thumb').forEach(t => {
    t.addEventListener('click', () => {
      document.querySelectorAll('.thumb').forEach(x => x.classList.remove('active'));
      document.querySelectorAll('.viewer-pane').forEach(x => x.classList.remove('active'));
      t.classList.add('active');
      document.getElementById(t.dataset.pane).classList.add('active');
    });
  });
</script>

</body>
</html>
